    • create

      public static final DocumentParser create(Class<? extends DocumentParser> cls, Reader in)
      Creates a new DocumentParser.

      It assumes the DocumentParser has a single-parameter constructor which takes a Reader as input.

      Parameters:
      cls - the class of the document parser to be instantiated.
      in - the reader to the document(s) to be parsed.
      Returns:
      a new instance of DocumentParser for the given class.
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if cls and/or in are null.
      IllegalStateException - if something goes wrong in instantiating the class.
